title: Coast to Coast AM & Art Bell Dreamland (RARE)

CLASSIC C2CAM & AB Dreamland

Art Bell Dreamland_From 1994 & 1995

These mp3s are converted from cassette tape.  Mostly these cassette tapes are around14-15 years old.

These AB Dreamland shows are redo&#039;s.  I had previously converted them using a very poor method.  Which 
each of the files was around 30-50mb&#039;s.  Each of these files are around 5-10mb&#039;s.  The sound quality of these mp3&#039;s
range from 5-9 (in my opinion).  Pretty good sound given the age of the original tapes.
